Optimum Funds
We're pleased to say that the Optimum Funds are managed by some of the most respected and successful money managers in the industry. 
Macquarie Investment Management is the manager and distributor of the Optimum Funds, and each fund is designed to be advised or sub-advised by multiple managers with complementary investment styles. 
Each manager's unique investment philosophy attempts to provide assurance that your portfolio will not be unduly influenced in any one direction. This approach is commonly found in institutional portfolios where using complementary managers may provide greater diversification and attempts to smooth out volatility. 


Need more? 
