Optimum Fund Trust - Optimum Fixed Income Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 22, 2017 5:50 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Optimum Fund Trust - Optimum Fixed Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Optimum Fund Trust - Optimum Fixed Income Fund is an open ended fixed income mutual fund launched and managed by Delaware Management Business Trust. The fund is co-managed by Pacific Investment Management Company LLC. It invests in fixed income markets of the United States. The fund primarily invests in investment grade fixed income securities issued or guaranteed by the U.S. government or its agencies or instrumentalities, corporate debt securities, taxable and tax-exempt municipal securities, and mortgage-backed and asset-backed securities that are rated BBB- or higher by S&P or Baa3 or higher by Moody's and with varying maturities. It focuses on factors such as interest rates, currency ex...
Optimum Fund Trust - Optimum Fixed Income Fund is an open ended fixed income mutual fund launched and managed by Delaware Management Business Trust. The fund is co-managed by Pacific Investment Management Company LLC. It invests in fixed income markets of the United States. The fund primarily invests in investment grade fixed income securities issued or guaranteed by the U.S. government or its agencies or instrumentalities, corporate debt securities, taxable and tax-exempt municipal securities, and mortgage-backed and asset-backed securities that are rated BBB- or higher by S&P or Baa3 or higher by Moody's and with varying maturities. It focuses on factors such as interest rates, currency exchange rates, the economy, quality, sector, interest rate or maturity, financial markets and the evaluation of economic and market conditions, and its assessment of the returns and potential for appreciation that can be achieved from investments in each of the sectors to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Barclays U.S. Aggregate Index. It employs proprietary research to create its portfolio. Optimum Fund Trust - Optimum Fixed Income Fund was formed on August 1, 2003 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


2005 Market StreetOne Commerce SquarePhiladelphia, PA 19103-7094United StatesFounded in 2003



Phone: 215-255-2300

Fax: 215-255-2194

www.delawareinvestments.com/optimum-funds/products/optimum-fixed-income-fund.aspx







